<lb n="0543a21"/>
<lb n="0543a22"/><head type="no">No. 740</head>
<lb n="0543a23"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0543013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0543013"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>頞多和多耆經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0543a24"/>
<lb n="0543a25"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0543014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【宮】，人＋（名）【明】</note><app n="0543014"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">人名</rdg></app>今附西晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0543a26"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在為耶國時有多樹木處。與
<lb n="0543a27"/>眾比丘僧俱。比丘有五百人。月十五日盛<note n="0543015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝湯【宮】</note><app n="0543015"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">湯</rdg></app>
<lb n="0543a28"/>時。夜半寂然安靜。比丘僧自相難問。時栴檀
<lb n="0543a29"/>調弗天人。持天形狀威神光耀來。直前趣佛。
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0740.0543b" n="0543b"/>
<lb n="0543b01"/><note n="0543016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前以後＝至佛前已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前以後＝至佛前已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543016"><lem>前以後</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">至佛前已</rdg></app>悉脫身上珍寶著一面。但<note n="0543017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">披＝被【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">披＝被【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543017"><lem>披</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">被</rdg></app>一領
<lb n="0543b02"/>衣。前以頭面著佛足禮畢。問佛言。諸可過去
<lb n="0543b03"/>佛正覺弟子有經。<note n="0543018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔經〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔經〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543018"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>名頞多和多<note n="0543019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耆＋（經）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耆＋（經）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543019"><lem>耆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">耆經</rdg></app>。佛弟
<lb n="0543b04"/>子今亦復說是頞多和多耆經。願佛為我說
<lb n="0543b05"/>是經。當使弟子奉持。佛默然不<note n="0543020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＋（而）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應＋（而）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543020"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">應而</rdg></app>。栴檀調
<lb n="0543b06"/>弗。稽首而&CB00230;坐。佛即為比丘僧說經言。我為
<lb n="0543b07"/>若說頞多和多耆經。皆聽著心中。念之勿得
<lb n="0543b08"/>忘。比丘言。願佛說。我皆當受經戒。佛言。布
<lb n="0543b09"/>施有八事。何謂為八。愚癡人布施。但布施不
<lb n="0543b10"/>知其恩善所在。既布施不達世間無有常。癡
<lb n="0543b11"/>人持作常世間苦無極。愚人持作樂世間。所
<lb n="0543b12"/>有愚人言。是我所有可常得。世間人皆顛倒
<lb n="0543b13"/>不淨臭處惡露。愚人用作好。不知作善得善。
<lb n="0543b14"/>作惡得惡。愚人施與人。不知其人德深淺。持
<lb n="0543b15"/>善心施與得道者。<note n="0543021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋福【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（其）＋福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543021"><lem>福</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">其福</rdg></app>不可量。</p>
<lb n="0543b16"/><p>佛告諸比丘。何以知愚人不知。布施有十因
<lb n="0543b17"/>緣。何等為十。愚人布施<note n="0543022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不知〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不知〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543022"><lem>不知</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為尊自用<note n="0543023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所＝不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543023"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不</rdg></app>
<lb n="0543b18"/>與者得善。愚人<note n="0543024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（以）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（以）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543024"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不以</rdg></app>至心施與人也。愚人既施
<lb n="0543b19"/>與人<note n="0543025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔與〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔與〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543025"><lem>與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>時不敬重。不自手與。傳教人與施。
<lb n="0543b20"/>人<note n="0543026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（久）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（久）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543026"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不久</rdg></app>欲望其福。不即得其福者。自用<note n="0543027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忘＝亡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忘＝亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543027"><lem>忘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亡</rdg></app>其
<lb n="0543b21"/>福。愚人施與佛辟支佛阿羅漢。不能自知其
<lb n="0543b22"/>福大。愚人施與。不信佛辟支佛阿羅漢阿那
<lb n="0543b23"/>含斯陀含須陀洹。皆用為棄<note n="0543028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">損＝捐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">損＝捐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543028"><lem>損</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">捐</rdg></app>。無有後生。
<lb n="0543b24"/>愚人施與。<note n="0543029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲但＝但欲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲但＝但欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543029"><lem>欲但</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">但欲</rdg></app>得名字。欲使人稱譽。是為
<lb n="0543b25"/>愚人布施。佛說經已。栴檀調弗。及諸比丘。皆
<lb n="0543b26"/>歡喜。前為佛作禮。</p></div1>
<lb n="0543b27"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><title>佛說頞多和多耆經</title></jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>
